flowchart LR
  Pack[Knowledge pack zip or root] --> Preflight[Archive preflight guardrails]
  Preflight --> Validate[Strict or partial schema validation]
  Validate --> CrossRefs[Cross-reference validation]
  CrossRefs --> Import[Structured SQLite import]

  subgraph RuntimeConnection[Runtime connection repair]
    Import --> CurriculumTables[(curriculum topics skills task types)]
    Import --> TaskBank[(task_bank_tasks)]
    CurriculumTables --> Resolver[DB-backed CurriculumService]
    Resolver --> Unknown[unknown or clarify when confidence is low]
    Resolver --> Context[topic skill task type verifier kind]
    TaskBank --> SelectTask[TaskBankService.selectTask]
    Context --> SelectTask
    SelectTask --> LessonTasks[(lesson_tasks)]
    LessonTasks --> Verifier[MathVerifierService]
    Verifier --> Attempts[(student_attempts)]
    Attempts --> Mastery[(mastery_evidence)]
  end

  subgraph RagSync[RAG sync hardening]
    Pack --> RagPaths[Current pack Markdown paths]
    RagPaths --> Reconcile[Reconcile active source paths]
    Reconcile --> Upload[Upload or skip changed files]
    Upload --> Attach[Attach to vector store]
    Attach --> WaitReady[Wait for indexing ready when enabled]
    WaitReady --> Cleanup[Detach retired or superseded files]
    Cleanup --> KnowledgeFiles[(knowledge_files)]
  end

  subgraph Recovery[Ledger and recovery]
    Validate --> Ledger[(knowledge_pack_imports)]
    Reconcile --> Jobs[(knowledge_pack_sync_jobs)]
    Jobs --> Recover[Retry and recovery command]
    Recover --> Ledger
    Recover --> KnowledgeFiles
  end

  Mastery --> Policy[LessonPolicy goal completion]
  Policy --> Tutor[Structured tutor response]
